criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. Patients with pulmonary nodules scheduled for thoracoscopic surgery;

          2. Age ≥ 18 and ≤ 75, regardless of gender;

          3. Understand and agree to participate in this study and sign the informed consent form.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. Patients who have previously received EA treatment;

          2. Patients with skin infection at acupoints;

          3. Patients with nerve injury of upper or lower limbs;

          4. Those who have participated or are participating in other clinical trials one month
             before enrollment.
